course_title: Analysis of Complex Health Systems for Populations and Organizations
course_description: This course is a synthesis and review of theories and principles related to complex systems in health care delivery, health related organizations, and populations emphasizing the interplay among micro-, meso-, and macro-systems within the ecological framework.
